{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "help-pr-user-type4-address-crud",
    "name": "Help PR - User Type 4 Address CRUD",
    "description": "Standalone collection for customer (user type 4) mobile address APIs.\n\nFlow:\n1) Create Address\n2) Update Address\n3) Delete Address\n\nAuth:\n- Use Bearer token of a customer account (type = 4).\n- Set collection variable {{customerToken}}.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Create Address (Type 4)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "try {",
              "  const j = pm.response.json();",
              "  const id = j?.data?._id || j?.data?.data?._id;",
              "  if (id) pm.collectionVariables.set('addressId', String(id));",
              "} catch (e) {}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [
            {
              "key": "token",
              "value": "{{customerToken}}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"state_id\": \"{{stateId}}\",\n  \"city_id\": \"{{cityId}}\",\n  \"area_id\": \"{{areaId}}\",\n  \"pincode\": \"{{pincode}}\",\n  \"address\": \"Flat 302, Green Heights, 5th Main Road\"\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/user/addresses",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "mobile",
            "user",
            "addresses"
          ]
        },
        "description": "POST /api/mobile/user/addresses\n\nRequired body fields:\n- state_id (ObjectId)\n- city_id (ObjectId)\n- area_id (ObjectId)\n- pincode (string from selected area)\n- address (string)\n\nOn success, this request stores response address _id into {{addressId}}."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Update Address (Type 4)",
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [
            {
              "key": "token",
              "value": "{{customerToken}}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "method": "PUT",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"address\": \"Flat 402, Green Heights, 5th Main Road\"\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/user/addresses/{{addressId}}",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "mobile",
            "user",
            "addresses",
            "{{addressId}}"
          ]
        },
        "description": "PUT /api/mobile/user/addresses/:id\n\n- Send at least one of: state_id, city_id, area_id, pincode, address.\n- If you update any location field (state/city/area/pincode), send all 4 together.\n- For address-only edit, body with only address is valid."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete Address (Type 4)",
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [
            {
              "key": "token",
              "value": "{{customerToken}}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "method": "DELETE",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/user/addresses/{{addressId}}",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "mobile",
            "user",
            "addresses",
            "{{addressId}}"
          ]
        },
        "description": "DELETE /api/mobile/user/addresses/:id"
      },
      "response": []
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "customerToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "stateId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "cityId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "areaId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "pincode",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "addressId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ]
}
